g the nerves. This is  its use. Those who continue drinking till wine inflames them, abase  this mercy of God.}}</ref> [[Thomas_Coke_(bishop)|Thomas Coke]]) and [[Baptists|Baptists]] ([[John_Gill_(theologian)|John Gill]] and [[John_Bunyan|John Bunyan]]).
